B.afm=new A.c8("Change to passive voice","The teacher explains the lesson.","The lesson is explained by the teacher.","Object becomes subject, verb to be + past participle","Dalam passive voice, objek menjadi subjek dan kata kerja berubah menjadi to be + past participle.")
B.afq=new A.c8("Change to passive voice","Someone has stolen my bicycle.","My bicycle has been stolen.","Has been + past participle, object becomes subject","Present perfect passive: has/have + been + past participle.")
B.afC=new A.c8("Change to passive voice","They will announce the results tomorrow.","The results will be announced tomorrow.","Will be + past participle",'Future passive: will + be + past participle. "The results" menjadi subjek baru.')
B.afo=new A.c8("Change to active voice","The cake was baked by my grandmother.","My grandmother baked the cake.",'Subject comes from "by", verb changes to active form','Active voice: subjek (dari "by phrase") + kata kerja aktif + objek.')
B.afJ=new A.c8("Change to passive voice","The manager is reviewing the report.","The report is being reviewed by the manager.","Is being + past participle (continuous passive)","Present continuous passive: is/are + being + past participle.")
B.afv=new A.c8("Change to reported speech",'"I will come tomorrow," he said.',"He said that he would come the next day.","Will -> would, tomorrow -> the next day","Direct ke indirect: will berubah menjadi would, time expression berubah (tomorrow -> the next day).")
B.afi=new A.c8("Change to reported speech",'"I am learning English," she said.',"She said that she was learning English.","Present continuous -> past continuous (was learning)","Reported speech: am/is/are -> was/were. Tense mundur satu tingkat.")
B.afy=new A.c8("Change to reported speech",'"I have finished my homework," Tom said.',"Tom said that he had finished his homework.","Have -> Had (past perfect)","Present perfect berubah menjadi past perfect (had + past participle).")
B.afM=new A.c8("Change to reported speech",'"I visited Paris last year," John said.',"John said that he had visited Paris the year before.","Past simple -> past perfect, last year -> the year before","Past simple bisa berubah menjadi past perfect. Time expression berubah: last year -> the year before.")
B.afK=new A.c8("Change to reported speech",'"Do not touch the fire," she warned.',"She warned us not to touch the fire.","Imperative becomes infinitive construction","Perintah dalam reported speech berubah menjadi to-infinitive: told/warned + object + not to + verb.")
B.afH=new A.c8("Complete with the correct conditional","If I ___ (be) rich, I would buy a yacht.","If I were rich, I would buy a yacht.",'Use "were" for all subjects in type 2','Conditional type 2 (unreal present): If + past simple, would + base verb. Gunakan "were" untuk semua subjek.')
B.afA=new A.c8("Complete with the correct conditional","If it ___ (rain) tomorrow, we will cancel the trip.","If it rains tomorrow, we will cancel the trip.","Type 1: If + present simple, will + verb","Conditional type 1 (possible): If + present simple, will + base verb.")
B.afI=new A.c8("Complete with the correct conditional","If she ___ (study) harder, she would have passed.","If she had studied harder, she would have passed.","Type 3: If + past perfect, would have + past participle","Conditional type 3 (unreal past): If + past perfect, would have + past participle.")
B.afL=new A.c8("Rewrite using unless","If you do not practice, you will not improve.","Unless you practice, you will not improve.","Unless = if not",'"Unless" adalah negation dari "if". "If not" bisa diganti dengan "unless".')
B.afe=new A.c8("Rewrite as a zero conditional","Water freezes when it is cold enough.","If water gets cold enough, it freezes.","Both clauses use present simple","Zero conditional: If + present simple, present simple. Kedua bagian sama-sama present tense.")
B.afw=new A.c8('Rewrite using "so...that"',"It was a very hot day. We could not sleep.","It was so hot that we could not sleep.","So + adjective/adverb + that",'"So...that" digunakan untuk menunjukkan akibat/konsekuensi dari tingkat tertentu.')
B.afg=new A.c8('Rewrite using "such...that"',"She is a very talented singer. Everyone admires her.","She is such a talented singer that everyone admires her.","Such + (a/an) + adjective + noun + that",'"Such...that" digunakan dengan noun. "Such a talented singer" diikuti that clause.')
B.afz=new A.c8('Rewrite using "too...to"',"He is very old. He cannot work.","He is too old to work.","Too + adjective + to + verb",'"Too...to" menunjukkan bahwa sesuatu melebihi batas yang diperlukan.')
B.afF=new A.c8('Rewrite using "enough to"',"The box was very heavy. We could not lift it.","The box was not heavy enough for us to lift.","Not + adjective + enough + to + verb",'"Enough to" digunakan setelah adjective untuk menunjukkan kapabilitas.')
B.afk=new A.c8('Rewrite using "enough...to"',"She is very tall. She can reach the top shelf.","She is tall enough to reach the top shelf.","Adjective + enough + to + verb",'"Enough...to" menunjukkan bahwa sesuatu memenuhi syarat yang diperlukan.')
B.afs=new A.c8("Combine using relative pronoun","The man is standing there. He teaches mathematics.","The man who is standing there teaches mathematics.",'Use "who" for people as subject','"Who" digunakan sebagai subject dalam relative clause.')
B.aff=new A.c8("Combine using relative pronoun","The book is on the table. You lent it to me.","The book which you lent to me is on the table.",'Use "which" for things as object','"Which" digunakan untuk benda, bisa sebagai object dalam relative clause.')
B.afN=new A.c8("Combine using relative pronoun","The city is very beautiful. I was born there.","The city where I was born is very beautiful.",'Use "where" for places','"Where" digunakan untuk tempat, menggantikan "in which" atau "at which".')
B.afl=new A.c8("Combine using relative pronoun","The reason is unclear. She was absent.","The reason why she was absent is unclear.",'Use "why" for reasons','"Why" digunakan untuk alasan, menggantikan "for which".')
B.afn=new A.c8("Rewrite without relative clause","The student who won the prize is my cousin.","My cousin is the student who won the prize.","Rephrase to keep the information","Relative clause yang identifying (mendefinisikan) tidak bisa dihapus. Kita perlu merekonstruksi kalimat.")
