B.afp=new A.c8("Rewrite using causative","A mechanic repaired my car yesterday.","I had my car repaired yesterday.","Have/get + object + past participle",'Causative "have something done" menunjukkan bahwa seseorang meminta orang lain untuk melakukan sesuatu.')
